title: MLB suspends Los Angeles' Chase Utley for Games 3 and 4 of the NL Division Series
text:
MLB suspends Los Angeles’ Chase Utley for Games 3 and 4 of the NL Division Series By - Associated Press - Sunday, October 11, 2015 
NEW YORK (AP) - MLB suspends Los Angeles’ Chase Utley for Games 3 and 4 of the NL Division Series.
